#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:9
msgid "明天是今天的延续，今天是明天的提前。"
msgstr "Tomorrow extends today; today previews tomorrow."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:10
msgid "中低电量，也要推进一个最小动作。"
msgstr "Even at low power, move one smallest action forward."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:11
msgid "不要创造刺激，先创造价值。"
msgstr "Do not create stimulation; create value first."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:12
msgid "高维空转会成为利息税。"
msgstr "High-level spinning becomes interest tax."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:13
msgid "接地，不是放弃理想，是把理想接到地面。"
msgstr ""
"Grounding is not giving up ideals; it is connecting ideals to the ground."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:14
msgid "现在不是证明自己伟大，而是完成下一步。"
msgstr ""
"This is not the time to prove greatness; it is time to finish the next step."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:15
msgid "把当前状态记录下来，就是重新夺回方向盘。"
msgstr "Recording the current state is taking back the steering wheel."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:16
msgid "疲惫时不要规划人生，先完成一个小动作。"
msgstr "When tired, do not plan your life; finish one small action first."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:17
msgid "真正的执行，不依赖情绪同意。"
msgstr "Real execution does not depend on emotional permission."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:18
msgid "空想可以点火，但落地才能发电。"
msgstr "Imagination can ignite, but landing generates power."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:19
msgid "不要等状态好，状态是在行动中恢复的。"
msgstr "Do not wait for a good state; state recovers through action."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:20
msgid "先把手放到事情上，心会慢慢跟上。"
msgstr "Put your hands on the work first; the heart will follow slowly."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:21
msgid "焦虑不是命令，它只是噪音。"
msgstr "Anxiety is not a command; it is only noise."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:22
msgid "今天不用赢世界，只要赢一次漂移。"
msgstr "You do not need to beat the world today; beat one drift."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:23
msgid "能量低，就把任务切到更小。"
msgstr "When energy is low, cut the task smaller."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:24
msgid "接地的第一步，是说清我现在在干嘛。"
msgstr "The first step of grounding is saying clearly what I am doing now."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:25
msgid "记录不是浪费时间，记录是在校准方向。"
msgstr "Recording is not wasting time; recording calibrates direction."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:26
msgid "不必立刻强大，但要立刻靠近现实。"
msgstr ""
"You do not need to be strong immediately, but you need to approach reality "
"immediately."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:27
msgid "世界不会因为你想明白才开始运转。"
msgstr ""
"The world does not wait for you to think everything through before it turns."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:28
msgid "先做可见的一步，再谈宏大的结构。"
msgstr "Do one visible step first, then discuss grand structures."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:29
msgid "把想法压进动作里，它才会变成力量。"
msgstr "Press the idea into action; only then does it become force."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:30
msgid "拖延不是失败，但不观察拖延会变成系统。"
msgstr "Delay is not failure, but unobserved delay becomes a system."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:31
msgid "今天的最小闭环，就是明天的支点。"
msgstr "Today's smallest closed loop is tomorrow's support point."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:32
msgid "不要追求完美启动，追求真实启动。"
msgstr "Do not seek a perfect start; seek a real start."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:33
msgid "当前这一分钟，比想象中的未来更有权重。"
msgstr "This current minute has more weight than the imagined future."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:34
msgid "不要用复杂性保护逃避。"
msgstr "Do not use complexity to protect avoidance."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:35
msgid "把混乱写下来，混乱就开始失去权力。"
msgstr "Write the chaos down, and chaos begins to lose power."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:36
msgid "接地值下降时，先回到手边的任务。"
msgstr "When grounding drops, return first to the task at hand."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:37
msgid "能量值不是道德评分，它只是仪表盘。"
msgstr "Energy is not a moral score; it is a dashboard."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:38
msgid "心情值不是结论，它只是天气。"
msgstr "Mood is not a conclusion; it is weather."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:39
msgid "低心情时，不要做终局判断。"
msgstr "When mood is low, do not make final judgments."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:40
msgid "低能量时，不要否定整个人生。"
msgstr "When energy is low, do not deny your whole life."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:41
msgid "低接地时，不要相信宏大冲动。"
msgstr "When grounding is low, do not trust grand impulses."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:42
msgid "先问：我现在能完成什么？"
msgstr "First ask: what can I finish now?"

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:43
msgid "事情不是靠感动完成的，是靠连续动作完成的。"
msgstr ""
"Things are not completed by being moved; they are completed by continuous "
"actions."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:44
msgid "少一点解释自己，多一点移动棋子。"
msgstr "Explain yourself less; move pieces more."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:45
msgid "真正的自由，来自可重复的执行能力。"
msgstr "True freedom comes from repeatable execution."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:46
msgid "把今天变成证据，而不是幻想。"
msgstr "Turn today into evidence, not fantasy."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:47
msgid "你不需要燃烧，你需要稳定供电。"
msgstr "You do not need to burn; you need stable power."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:48
msgid "别让大目标吃掉小动作。"
msgstr "Do not let big goals eat small actions."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:49
msgid "现实不是敌人，现实是接口。"
msgstr "Reality is not the enemy; reality is the interface."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:50
msgid "最好的灵感，是能进入下一步的灵感。"
msgstr "The best inspiration is inspiration that can enter the next step."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:51
msgid "不要把思考当成完成。"
msgstr "Do not mistake thinking for finishing."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:52
msgid "不要把紧张当成努力。"
msgstr "Do not mistake tension for effort."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:53
msgid "不要把收藏当成学习。"
msgstr "Do not mistake collecting for learning."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:54
msgid "不要把计划当成推进。"
msgstr "Do not mistake planning for progress."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:55
msgid "不要把焦虑当成责任感。"
msgstr "Do not mistake anxiety for responsibility."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:56
msgid "不要把兴奋当成成果。"
msgstr "Do not mistake excitement for results."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:57
msgid "真正的进展，会留下痕迹。"
msgstr "Real progress leaves traces."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:58
msgid "今天至少留下一条可验证的痕迹。"
msgstr "Leave at least one verifiable trace today."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:59
msgid "没有闭环的忙碌，会慢慢变成幻觉。"
msgstr "Busyness without closure slowly becomes hallucination."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:60
msgid "一件事落地，胜过十个宏大判断。"
msgstr "One thing landed beats ten grand judgments."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:61
msgid "先交付一个粗糙版本，再优化尊严。"
msgstr "Deliver a rough version first; optimize dignity later."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:62
msgid "把任务做到能被别人看见。"
msgstr "Make the task visible to others."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:63
msgid "把想法做到能被自己复盘。"
msgstr "Make the idea reviewable by yourself."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:64
msgid "重复不是低级，重复是系统成形的方式。"
msgstr "Repetition is not low-level; repetition is how systems form."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:65
msgid "节奏比爆发更可靠。"
msgstr "Rhythm is more reliable than bursts."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:66
msgid "你不是没方向，你是需要重新对焦。"
msgstr "You are not directionless; you need to refocus."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:67
msgid "漂移不可怕，不回看才可怕。"
msgstr "Drifting is not scary; never looking back is."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:68
msgid "观察自己，不是审判自己。"
msgstr "Observing yourself is not judging yourself."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:69
msgid "状态差时，降低难度，不要取消行动。"
msgstr "When the state is poor, lower the difficulty; do not cancel action."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:70
msgid "把自己从情绪里捞出来，放回任务里。"
msgstr "Lift yourself out of emotion and put yourself back into the task."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:71
msgid "不要在脑内开会，打开文件。"
msgstr "Do not hold meetings in your head; open the file."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:72
msgid "不要在脑内创业，发出一个请求。"
msgstr "Do not start a company in your head; send one request."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:73
msgid "不要在脑内复盘，写下一句话。"
msgstr "Do not review in your head; write one sentence."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:74
msgid "把注意力从评价切回动作。"
msgstr "Move attention from evaluation back to action."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:75
msgid "能做一点，就先做一点。"
msgstr "If you can do a little, do a little first."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:76
msgid "一点点不是安慰，一点点是入口。"
msgstr "A little is not comfort; a little is an entrance."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:77
msgid "入口比宏图重要。"
msgstr "The entrance matters more than the grand map."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:78
msgid "启动比姿势重要。"
msgstr "Starting matters more than posture."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:79
msgid "完成比解释重要。"
msgstr "Finishing matters more than explanation."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:80
msgid "复盘比自责重要。"
msgstr "Review matters more than self-blame."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:81
msgid "今天的执行，是给明天的自己铺路。"
msgstr "Today's execution lays road for tomorrow's self."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:82
msgid "人会漂，系统要拉你回来。"
msgstr "People drift; the system should pull you back."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:83
msgid "当你不知道做什么，就记录现在。"
msgstr "When you do not know what to do, record now."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:84
msgid "当你想逃避，就缩小任务。"
msgstr "When you want to avoid, shrink the task."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:85
msgid "当你想证明，就先交付。"
msgstr "When you want to prove, deliver first."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:86
msgid "当你想放弃，就先暂停判断。"
msgstr "When you want to give up, pause judgment first."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:87
msgid "当你想空转，就问现实接口在哪里。"
msgstr "When you want to spin, ask where the reality interface is."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:88
msgid "别急着寻找意义，先制造一个可用结果。"
msgstr "Do not rush to find meaning; make a usable result first."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:89
msgid "意义不是想出来的，是被行动压实的。"
msgstr "Meaning is not imagined; it is compacted by action."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:90
msgid "稳定的小动作，会慢慢长成命运。"
msgstr "Stable small actions slowly grow into fate."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:91
msgid "让今天有一个干净的切口。"
msgstr "Give today a clean incision."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:92
msgid "让任务小到无法拒绝。"
msgstr "Make the task too small to refuse."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:93
msgid "让记录诚实到无法欺骗。"
msgstr "Make the record honest enough that it cannot deceive."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:94
msgid "让系统温柔到可以持续。"
msgstr "Make the system gentle enough to continue."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:95
msgid "让行动具体到可以开始。"
msgstr "Make the action concrete enough to begin."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:96
msgid "别和疲惫争辩，给它一个小任务。"
msgstr "Do not argue with fatigue; give it a small task."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:97
msgid "别和焦虑辩论，给它一个时间盒。"
msgstr "Do not debate anxiety; give it a timebox."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:98
msgid "别和空虚对抗，给它一个现实动作。"
msgstr "Do not fight emptiness; give it a real action."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:99
msgid "能量会波动，结构要稳定。"
msgstr "Energy will fluctuate; structure should stay stable."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:100
msgid "心情会波动，记录要稳定。"
msgstr "Mood will fluctuate; recording should stay stable."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:101
msgid "接地会波动，提醒要稳定。"
msgstr "Grounding will fluctuate; reminders should stay stable."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:102
msgid "每一次记录，都是一次返航。"
msgstr "Every record is a return voyage."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:103
msgid "每一次提交，都是一次落子。"
msgstr "Every submission is a move placed."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:104
msgid "每一次接地，都是一次回到现实。"
msgstr "Every grounding is a return to reality."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:105
msgid "不要轻看两分钟，它能切断一整天的漂移。"
msgstr ""
"Do not underestimate two minutes; it can cut off a whole day of drifting."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:106
msgid "观察不是为了控制一切，而是为了不被一切拖走。"
msgstr ""
"Observation is not to control everything, but to avoid being dragged away by "
"everything."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:107
msgid "今天只问三个数和一句话。"
msgstr "Today asks only three numbers and one sentence."

#: src/QuoteProvider.cpp:108
msgid "你现在在哪里？你正在做什么？你还要不要回来？"
msgstr "Where are you now? What are you doing? Do you still want to return?"

